{"tid":1040752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想知澳門人點睇香港派錢","createTime":"2019-02-28T10:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T09:52:28.000Z","uid":37458,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5d893232b6f065672cbde586f3dc57d2a457f7ef","tid":1040752,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 澳門年年派 <br />\n香港第一次派6000<br />\n第二次4000<br />\n依家好似話有可能2000<br />\n想知澳門人點恥笑香港人幾低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd181d7057d6262591a8ae58fadecfcd13d7a90","tid":1040752,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3505f6666a6627166bf5040c74f86751e72102ac","tid":1040752,"uid":476,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"攞完之後過去香港痴福利痴教學先係王道<br />\n詳情問關蛇"},{"pid":"f5e325e3f728d87a429ea33432ccb7857befa9ef","tid":1040752,"uid":45368,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"食哂兩邊茶飯既先係最後贏家"},{"pid":"6e2fde01909a5789dbacf665f3e0db6f336f5b73","tid":1040752,"uid":224561,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恥笑就唔會<br />\n但會覺得香港人唔抵<br />\n會覺得港共係賣緊香港<br />\n<br />\n澳門人鍾意成日痴/欣賞香港<br />\n(有啲香港人會反感都正常嘅)<br />\n多多少少都係因為以前香港比澳門好好多<br />\n<br />\n但講真<br />\n香港係退步緊<br />\n係好快嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n老實講香港絕對有能力去做得比澳門好<br />\n但唔去做<br />\n<br />\n攞嗰4000都咁難<br />\n攞到錢都過咗一段時間<br />\n小小恩惠當大賞<br />\n畀錢中共就快過問財仔借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6360f8ef95d92e4f1cc0d0480192779af490611","tid":1040752,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dfdaca29e43aa70b872f1d137